ment and portfolio management roles with several major wall street investment advisory and brokerage firms he is an experienced portfolio manager known for his strong commitment to intensive equity research on behalf of his clients “at midwest investment management” said mr vanden broeck “i collaborate with likeminded people who view fundamental security analysis as the foundation for stock selection we also share the view that owning stocks represents the partial ownership of a business” “in fact” mr vanden broeck added “we pride ourselves on owning the same investments as our clients it raises the threshold of examination” “we generate new investment ideas by spending countless hours reading periodicals company filings and other materials resulting in detailed analysis and disciplined valuations” mr vanden broeck noted “we identify facts that we really need to know and stick to companies whose economics we understand” mr vanden broeck holds a ba in economics from macalaster college in st paul minnesota and has completed additional course work at the university of parissorbonne he is a trustee of the ratner school in pepper pike and past treasurer of the shaker lakes nature center he resides with his family in shaker heights mr vanden broeck can be reached at email address protected by javascript please enable javascript to contact me or   midwest investment management  cleveland ohio  portfolio management and investment advice  introduction introduction there are many reasons why people seek and need the services of a professional investment management firm norman f klopp managing partner whatever your reason its a decision that requires very serious thoughtful evaluation and consideration thats why you should get to know our firm the partners are seasoned experienced investment professionals prior to forming the company in january  they worked together as a team for many years the firm is  owned by its partners who collectively have over  years of investment ma